  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a paella pan over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in diced tomatoes, raisins, fermented jang, smoked paprika, and saffron, cooking for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the rice and stir to coat the grains with the sauce and oil.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and water, bringing the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat, add green peas, and sprinkle toasted walnuts, covering partially and simmering for 18 minutes until the rice absorbs the liquid.",
    "Stir gently and let the paella rest uncovered for 5 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
